overview: She's mistaken for a temp, filling in for a 'hot shot' Hollywood producer, but in no time learns the meaning of the word's casting couch! With some ball-bustin' anal scenes, threeways and girl/girl that'll bring you to your knees. Oy! Just another day for a little girl from the Queens.
tagline: Oy! What a schlep; so many men... ...So little time!
title: The Fanny
